果陣好似有日本人黎交流？</blockquote><br />\n卑彌呼有派人出使魏國<br />\n但嗰時應該係行朝鮮半島過嚟<br />\n以當時技術，要喺茫茫大海中搵咁細嘅琉球群島應該仲難過去日本本土</blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦<br />\n連邪馬台確實位置響邊到今日都仲未有定論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係九洲"},{"pid":"7094654d7b387fae350d63437073687e157b1943","tid":181001,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"東吳一直靠班土豪鄉紳撐住, 佢地理鳩得你咩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f79c425a09a1431c98d4c25a5d69e364e0bb19","tid":181001,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東吳一直靠班土豪鄉紳撐住, 佢地理鳩得你咩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到亡國果陣，土豪鄉紳一樣無運行。<br />\n<br />\n應該趁早移民"},{"pid":"63693eef6f34e0132b914f8ea85c2bed50df9ed9","tid":181001,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東吳一直靠班土豪鄉紳撐住, 佢地理鳩得你咩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到亡國果陣，土豪鄉紳一樣無運行。<br />\n<br />\n應該趁早移民</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成班一早準備好跳船la.<br />\n唔係班鄉紳, 天下未必歸晉. 班友只係唔想出錢, 邊個做皇帝理鳩得你.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfb90918e7c89367e6832d9b1e500bb404ef585","tid":181001,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東吳一直靠班土豪鄉紳撐住, 佢地理鳩得你咩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到亡國果陣，土豪鄉紳一樣無運行。<br />\n<br />\n應該趁早移民</blockquote><br />\n到時投降咪得囉，聽講魏國好愛才架"},{"pid":"4f4f389156628f2b34f3652f3bfd6ea80a6ebf70","tid":181001,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東吳一直靠班土豪鄉紳撐住, 佢地理鳩得你咩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到亡國果陣，土豪鄉紳一樣無運行。<br />\n<br />\n應該趁早移民</blockquote><br />\n到時投降咪得囉，聽講魏國好愛才架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歷史上真係等到蒙古人民先將班江南土豪徹底處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90bd3286ae17b16c0cf0933a33a3a31e8890cfe","tid":181001,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>東吳一直靠班土豪鄉紳撐住, 佢地理鳩得你咩.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到亡國果陣，土豪鄉紳一樣無運行。<br />\n<br />\n應該趁早移民</blockquote><br />\n到時投降咪得囉，聽講魏國好愛才架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n歷史上真係等到蒙古人民先將班江南土豪徹底處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以到明咪先可以北伐成功.<br />\n<br />\n香港班地產商都係賣港, 唔俾香港發圍罪魁禍首."},{"pid":"ea28fc10ebd596d52ea0f92829c9d468de653037","tid":181001,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"個陣都未有航海時代既經濟系統"}]}